From gavin.simpson at ucl.ac.uk  Wed May 18 18:48:04 2011
From: gavin.simpson at ucl.ac.uk (Gavin Simpson)
Date: Wed, 18 May 2011 17:48:04 +0100
Subject: [R-sig-eco] Error message in GAM
In-Reply-To: <BANLkTikz-dQ=jV9YkfTGgEYO5uBWmcUsMw@mail.gmail.com>
References: <BANLkTikz-dQ=jV9YkfTGgEYO5uBWmcUsMw@mail.gmail.com>
